original: Bergstrand, Carl-Erik, leg. läkare, Borås, f. 25/12/14 i Göteborg av lä-roviadj. Erik B. o. Elsa Witte. — Studiex. i Skara 33, med. kand. i Upps. 37, med. lic. i Sthlm 43. Tf. und iläk. v. Visby las. 43-44, v. med. avd. å Umeå las. 44-46, und iläk. v. med. avd. å centr ilas. i Borås fr. 46.
translated: Bergstrand, Carl-Erik, licensed physician, Borås, b. 25/12/14 in Gothenburg to clergyman Erik B. and Elsa Witte. - Studied in Skara until 1933, received Bachelor of Medicine from Uppsala University in 1937, and licensed as a physician in Stockholm in 1943. Served as acting assistant physician at Visby Hospital from 1943-1944, medical department assistant at Umeå Hospital from 1944-1946, and acting assistant physician at the medical department of Borås Central Hospital since 1946.
